  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a comparison of open surgery versus an endoscopic approach in condylar neck
      fractures; it will look at functional outcome, cosmetic outcome and patient satisfaction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The primary outcome measure is functional outcome based on the Helkimo dysfunction index.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
